@SalesApiStub_HostAddress = http://localhost:5234

### Request an OAuth access token
POST {{SalesApiStub_HostAddress}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=demo-client&client_secret=demo-secret&scope=sales:read

###
